[section#meta.unary
    [:en] Unary type traits
]

[para]
[:en]
This sub-clause contains templates that may be used to query the properties of a
type at compile time.

[para]
[:en]
Each of these templates shall be a UnaryTypeTrait ([#meta.rqmts]) with a
BaseCharacteristic of [`true_type] if the corresponding condition is true,
otherwise [`false_type].

